			Submited by:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:royal4@hotmail.com">Bloodstar Deathshado</a></font> 
			<font face="Verdana" size="1">On:&nbsp;7/12/2001 8:24:36 AM</font></b>
			<td nowrap bgcolor="#808080" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_silver.gif" align="right">
				<font face="Verdana" size="1"><b>Rank:&nbsp;&nbsp;</font>	
				<font face="Verdana" size="1">worst</font>
				<b><a href="javascript:openWindow(1,466197);"><font face="Verdana" size="1" >1</font></a></b>
				<b><a href="javascript:openWindow(2,466197);"><font face="Verdana" size="1" >2</font></a></b>
